Jag får "Invalid or corrupt authenticity information" på varje rar fil när jag försöker packa upp. Är det någon annan som fått detta fel?

Äh, det kanske inte är nåt problem...

Invalid or corrupt authenticity information. In this case, it merely means that the poster used an unregistered version of WinRAR with authenticity information enabled, so that the error recovery data is not saved. Usually this is not a problem and the file should extract just fine. Unless if the files fail the crc check when checking with SFV, in which case recovery method will not work and another repair method or replacement of the file is needed.
